<p>&#8216;Medical device manufacturers should put a plan in place for using the new &#8220;UKCA&#8221; mark on their products – despite new legislation being put forward to allow EU-derived ‘CE’ markings to continue to be relied upon when selling such products in Britain for years to come.&#8217;</p>
